    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>At UniShare, we believe quality education should be accessible. That’s why we built a platform where college seniors can share well-organized notes — verified and approved — so juniors can save time and prepare better.</p>

    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Seniors sign up and upload notes</li>
      <li>Admin verifies their identity via college ID</li>
      <li>Notes are categorized by subject and topic</li>
      <li>Juniors download, rate, and connect with seniors</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Why UniShare?</h2>
    <p>Unlike generic platforms, UniShare focuses on verified, college-specific content. Plus, you can directly chat with contributors for clarifications.</p>

    <h2>Get Involved</h2>
    <p>Join the UniShare community — whether you're uploading, learning, or helping someone succeed.</p>
